-- D.Telekom to buy SunCom Wireless for $1.6 bln
-- 
-- Mon Sep 17, 2007 1:57am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/09/17/us-deutschetelekom-suncom-idUSWEB763420070917

 

 FRANKFURT  (Reuters) - Deutsche Telekom ( DTEGn.DE ) said on Monday its mobile phone division T-Mobile USA had agreed to buy SunCom Wireless for about $1.6 billion. 

 Deutsche Telekom said in a statement it saw synergies from the transaction of about $1 billion and that it will also take on SunCom debt obligations of almost $800 million. The deal is expected to close in the first half of 2008.